        </item>
        <item>
            <title>《Death Stranding 2》10 分鐘預告片【有片睇】2025 正式推出</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/01/death-stranding-2-new-10-min-trailer/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=death-stranding-2-new-10-min-trailer</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/01/death-stranding-2-new-10-min-trailer/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 01 Feb 2024 05:44:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Death Stranding]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Death Stranding 2]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Hideo Kojima]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Kojima Production]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PlayStation 5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小島工作室]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小島秀夫]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1217989</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小島秀夫的 Kojima Productions 今日（2 月 1 日）在「State of Play」上發布《DEATH STRANDING 2》 （死亡擱淺 2）第一條預告片，簡述了遊戲故事內容，並分享了部分遊戲實際遊玩畫面。據悉遊戲將於 2025 年上市。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218169" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218190" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-6-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-6-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-6.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>長達 10 分鐘的預告片訊息量非常龐大，一開頭可見其承接了《Death Stranding》結局，Sam 完成任務後脫離了 Bridges，並加入了全新組織，以阻止「Death Stranding」繼續禍害人間。</p><p><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="Death Stranding 2 On The Beach - State of Play Announce Trailer | PS5 Games" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/wbLstJHlC4U?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></p><p>《DEATH STRANDING 2》繼續由 Norman Reedus 扮演主角 Sam，美國演員 Ellen Fanning、日本女星忽那汐裏和法國演員 Léa Seydoux 亦會在新作中演出。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218173" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-1-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-1-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-1.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218175" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-3-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-3-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-3.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在《Death Stranding 2》中，主角 Sam 會繼續拯救人類逃離滅亡的命運。預告片中還可以看見一名一身搖滾打扮的角色，使用電結他作武器。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218176" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-4-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-4-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-4.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218174" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-2-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-2-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-2.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-5-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-5-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-5.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218191" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-7-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-7-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/deathstranding2onthe-7.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>小島秀夫亦在自己的 X （前稱 Twitter）上分享了一系列《Death Stranding 2》角色的個人海報，但其亦表示現階段暫時不會透露遊戲角色名字。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218179" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gfnofxkagaao4sp-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gfnofxkagaao4sp-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gfnofxkagaao4sp-scaled.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218180" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gfnogxbuaawmsp-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gfnogxbuaawmsp-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gfnogxbuaawmsp-scaled.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1218181" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gfnoiazawaa97mq-326x580.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gfnoiazawaa97mq-326x580.jpg 326w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/gfnoiazawaa97mq-scaled.jpg 506w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 326px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" 